title: 'Pretty damn lucky': Fox News' Benjamin Hall gives update after Ukraine attack
content:
1. 'Pretty damn lucky': Fox News' Benjamin Hall gives update after Ukraine attack  New York Post
  2. Benjamin Hall gives health update following deadly Ukraine attack: 'I feel pretty damn lucky to be here'  Fox News
  3. Fox News correspondent Benjamin Hall shares first update since being wounded in Ukraine attack: "I feel pretty d*** lucky to be here"  CBS News
  4. Former 69 News reporter Alex Hogan continues to cover war in Ukraine, describes life in Lviv  69News WFMZ-TV
  5. Fox's Benjamin Hall, severely injured in Ukraine, pays tribute to colleagues killed in attack  The Hill
